g.text: To fully enjoy your life as Pirate in the PirateParty Switzerland in {PRINT_YEAR}, you have to pay your membership fee of {INVOICE_AMOUNT}.00 CHF within below data. Without paying you are only a sympathizer and you don't have any rights to vote on Pirate-Meetings, you'r not allowed to vote or proclaim vour opinion by PiVote nor can you officially politicize as a Pirate. With the Membership, you can fill also regional politics or national ones, which you can't as a sympathizer. Because politics isn't for free, we and your regional section will welcome every small donation, just adjust the amount below to your wants. Please note, that all donations above 500.00 CHF will be printed with names on the Website of the Pirateparty Switzerland. By the way, do we still have your correct data? If not, please send us your new ones, inclusive your Membernumber '{MEMBER_NUMBER}' to info@piratenpartei.ch The Pirateparty Switzerland and your Section give thanks for your due, and specially for your donation...

email.subject: Membership fee {PRINT_YEAR}, Piratenpartei Schweiz
email.content:
Ahoi {MEMBER_NAME}, attached you'l find your personal Membership-Invoice for {PRINT_YEAR}. To fully enjoy your life as a Pirate by the PirateParty Switzerland, you shoud pay this Invoice as fast as possible. The PDF shows all Data you need for the payment.
If you have any questions, just ask your regional board or the national one as well. Thanks for your contribution, financially and personally...
The Board from Piratenpartei Schweiz
NB: Dont forget the Pirate Summercongress in Aarau on 9/10 of June! If you aren't registered yet: https://my.piratenpartei.ch/pvreg/index.php More information you will find on http://www.piraten-aargau.ch/2012/04/03/piraten-sommerkongress/
